    "wireframeHtml": "<div class='lfm-pb-preview' style='font-family: \"Malgun Gothic\", \"Apple SD Gothic Neo\", sans-serif; background-color: #f7f7f7; padding: 12px 10px; max-width: 375px; margin: 0 auto; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);'><div style='background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #111; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px;'><div style='text-align: left;'><div style='font-size: 11px; color: #222; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 6px;'>구매 전 살뜰하게 챙기는 습관!</div><div style='font-size: 19px; color: #000; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 1;'>결제 혜택</div></div><div style='width: 32px; height: 32px; border: 1px solid #ddd; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: #fafafa; cursor: pointer;'><span style='font-size: 12px; color: #111; font-weight: bold; transform: scaleY(0.75);'>▲</span></div></div><div style='padding: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 12px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; text-align: left;'><h4 style='font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; color: #111; margin: 0 0 10px 0; letter-spacing: -0.5px;'>5월의 결제혜택(Subtitle)</h4><p style='font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.6; color: #444; margin: 0; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: -0.2px;'>대한민국의 경제질서는 개인과 기업의 경제상의 자유와 창의를 존중함을 기본으로 한다. 누구든지 체포 또는 구속을 당한 때에는 즉시 변호인의 조력을 받을 권리를 가진다. 다만, 형사피고인이 스스로 변호인을 구할 수 없을 때에는 법률이 정하는</p><div style='background-color: #e5e5e5; border: 1px dashed #cccccc; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 110px; margin-top: 16px;'><span style='font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #666; letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>IMG AREA</span></div></div><div style='background-color: #555555; padding: 24px 16px 20px 16px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; color: #ffffff;'><h3 style='font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #1c1c1c; margin: 0 0 12px 0; letter-spacing: -1px;'>1월의 결제 혜택</h3><div style='border-top: 1px solid #666666; margin-bottom: 20px;'></div><div style='margin-bottom: 24px;'><div style='display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px;'><span style='font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; color: #1c1c1c; font-family: \"Arial Black\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.5px;'>l.l:mall</span><span style='font-weight: 700; font-size: 13.5px; color: #1c1c1c; letter-spacing: -0.5px;'>신용카드 결제 혜택</span></div><div style='position: relative; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; padding: 8px 0;'><div style='width: 70px; height: 110px; border-radius: 6px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #112255 0%, #000822 100%); position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);'><div style='position: absolute; top: 8px; left: 8px; font-size: 5px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); transform: scale(0.8);'>l.l:mall</div><div style='position: absolute; bottom: 10px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, #e25822 10%, transparent 60%); opacity: 0.8;'></div><div style='position: absolute; top: 32px; left: 10px; width: 12px; height: 10px; background-color: #ffd700; border-radius: 2px; opacity: 0.8;'></div></div><div style='width: 70px; height: 110px; border-radius: 6px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d4d026 0%, #adb60e 100%); position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);'><div style='position: absolute; top: 8px; left: 8px; font-size: 5px; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); transform: scale(0.8);'>l.l:mall</div><div style='position: absolute; top: 40px; right: 8px; width: 30px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #2e8b57; transform: rotate(-30deg); opacity: 0.7;'></div><div style='position: absolute; top: 32px; left: 10px; width: 12px; height: 10px; background-color: #c0c0c0; border-radius: 2px; opacity: 0.8;'></div></div><div style='width: 70px; height: 110px; border-radius: 6px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #222222 0%, #0a0a0a 100%); position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);'><div style='position: absolute; top: 8px; left: 8px; font-size: 5px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); transform: scale(0.8);'>l.l:mall</div><div style='position: absolute; bottom: 12px; left: 8px; right: 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.1; text-align: left;'>l.l:<span style='font-size: 8px; font-weight: 400; display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);'>답게</span></div><div style='position: absolute; top: 32px; left: 10px; width: 12px; height: 10px; background-color: #ffd700; border-radius: 2px; opacity: 0.8;'></div></div><div style='position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); pointer-events: none;'><span style='font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); letter-spacing: -0.5px;'>이미지 자동 호출</span></div></div></div><div style='margin-bottom: 24px;'><div style='font-weight: 700; font-size: 13.5px; color: #1c1c1c; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;'>카카오페이 결제 혜택</div><div style='background-color: #5d5a15; border-radius: 2px; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);'><span style='font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; color: #000000; font-family: sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.2px;'>kakaopay</span><span style='font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; color: #000000; letter-spacing: -0.5px;'>1만원 즉시할인</span></div></div><div><ul style='list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 9.5px; line-height: 1.5; color: #b5b5b5; letter-spacing: -0.3px;'><li style='margin-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 8px; text-indent: -8px;'>- 제휴사 및 LFmall 사정에 의해 사전 고지 없이 변경 혹은 중단될 수 있습니다.</li><li style='padding-left: 8px; text-indent: -8px;'>- 예산 소진 시 주문서 또는 결제화면 내 즉시할인 금액이 표시되지 않으며, 즉시할인이 적용되지 않습니다.</li></ul><div style='display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; padding-top: 4px;'><span style='width: 5px; height: 5px; background-color: #000000; border-radius: 50%;'></span><span style='width: 5px; height: 5px; background-color: #888888; border-radius: 50%;'></span></div></div></div></div>"
